  "data": [
    [
      [
        ""
      ],
      [
        "No way… [Fabian] goes to Aukademi, my uni! The world is way too small. "
      ],
      [
        "Wait, you go to Aukademi? I study there too! What are you studying?"
      ],
      [
        "Game engineering and design, how about you?"
      ],
      [
        "What?!?! Me too!!! I- This is amazing! We should totally help each other now!"
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] nodded as I was excited about this new discovery. "
      ],
      [
        "I wasn’t surprised about not seeing him before tho, the class was fairly big enough."
      ],
      [
        "I was thinking of asking [Fabian] more questions about school,"
      ],
      [
        "when suddenly, he just jogs to stand in front of me and makes me cover my eyes."
      ],
      [
        "Wha-? What’s going on?"
      ],
      [
        "We’re getting close, so… bear with me."
      ],
      [
        "I huff, but ultimately decide to follow [Fabian]."
      ],
      [
        "We carefully walk for a little bit until he tells me to stop. "
      ],
      [
        "Alright, it’s not much but… I hope you like it."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] takes my hands off, and I see it."
      ],
      [
        "The sun shines brighter than ever as I see [his] surprise."
      ],
      [
        "And I really couldn’t help but feel my heart skip a beat as I saw it…"
      ],
      [
        "what they had prepared for me was an adorable picnic."
      ],
      [
        "It has sandwiches and grapes, how thoughtful! "
      ],
      [
        "Omg, [Fabian]! this is so cute, thank you!"
      ],
      [
        "M’lady."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] tips [his] imaginary fedora as [he] gestures to me to sit on the plaid blanket on the grass"
      ],
      [
        "I sit down and immediately grab one grape."
      ],
      [
        "I eat it and get surprised by a very sweet flavor all across my mouth. I close my eyes to savor it. "
      ],
      [
        "Just thinking about this moment alone is making me feel all fuzzy inside."
      ],
      [
        "Dating is so fun! I should’ve gone to a quick date event sooner. "
      ],
      [
        "Suddenly, [Fabian] wraps an arm around me and pulls me closer to [him]."
      ],
      [
        "[tn], I- uh… I’m not very good with words, but I just wanted to tell you..."
      ],
      [
        "that I’m very happy that you actually wanted to date me. I think that we’ll be a really good couple."
      ],
      [
        "Even if we have differences we haven’t discovered yet, I know we can make it through all of them."
      ],
      [
        "My heart skips a beat at the sudden honesty. "
      ],
      [
        "Leaves fall down around us as we look intently at each other’s eyes. "
      ],
      [
        "A mysterious force pulls us together slowly, as if we both were magnets."
      ],
      [
        "And we join our lips together in a soft and tender kiss. "
      ],
      [
        "Time seems to stop, until we both pull away from each other."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] brushes [his] hand against my cheek as [he] shows me a side smile. "
      ],
      [
        "I’ll take care of you, [tn]… Always and forever. I promise."
      ],
      [
        "I smile at [him] and lean against [him] as I close my eyes. "
      ],
      [
        "The sun was setting and I knew I would have to go back to my house soon… "
      ],
      [
        "But right now, with [Fabian] by my side, I feel like this moment will last forever"
      ],
      [
        "in my heart"
      ],
      [
        "My eyes flutter open as my alarm goes off."
      ],
      [
        "I turn it off with annoyance on my face, but as I recall what happened yesterday,"
      ],
      [
        "a smile is plastered on my face."
      ],
      [
        "That’s right, [Fabian] and I shared our very first kiss. "
      ],
      [
        "I quickly jump out of bed and get ready for class."
      ],
      [
        "Especially because now, [Fabian] and I are going to sit together. "
      ],
      [
        "After a while, I make my way to school and arrive earlier than usual."
      ],
      [
        "I scan the room and see [Fabian] seating in a usually empty pair of tables. "
      ],
      [
        "As I approach [him], I notice [he]’s holding a gaming console in [his] hands."
      ],
      [
        "[he] seems very into the game."
      ],
      [
        "A fireball suddenly hits his character and “Game over” can be seen in big red letters. "
      ],
      [
        "[He] leans on the table and groans, until [he] turns [his] head towards me and waves at me."
      ],
      [
        "Hey! You’re here…"
      ],
      [
        "Sorry if you saw my pathetic lack of mad skillz"
      ],
      [
        "I chuckle and give [Fabian] a kiss on [his] cheek as I sit down on the chair next to [him]."
      ],
      [
        "Nah, It’s okay…"
      ],
      [
        "I also lack skills sometimes, although It’s very rare, haha!"
      ],
      [
        "I smirk as I make my cocky remark,"
      ],
      [
        "but [Fabian] just looks at me with a blush as [he] seems to be at a loss of words."
      ],
      [
        "What’s wrong? Are you ok?"
      ],
      [
        "I-I Just, uh…"
      ],
      [
        "He looks away and covers half of [his] face with [his] hand."
      ],
      [
        "D- don’t kiss me in school… It’s weird."
      ],
      [
        "Even when [he] looks away with [his] annoyed face, I still think it’s kinda cute."
      ],
      [
        "I never thought I’d ever see him flustered like that."
      ],
      [
        "As I reach my hand towards him, the school bell rings to announce the start of classes."
      ],
      [
        "I roll my eyes and sit straight in my chair as I try to focus on class."
      ],
      [
        "But the reality is that my mind really doesn’t wanna pay attention to"
      ],
      [
        "whatever the teacher is saying."
      ],
      [
        "There is so much more to think about… Like [Fabian], or games, or food…"
      ],
      [
        "maybe pizza, or... A hot dog!"
      ],
      [
        "Yes, a hot dog. A hot dog with wings that flies straight into my mouth as I say Aaaaaaa-"
      ],
      [
        "YEOUCH!"
      ],
      [
        "I feel a flick near my eye as I yank my head towards who hit me."
      ],
      [
        "It was [Fabian], looking at me with amusement. "
      ],
      [
        "Lmaooooo, you should have looked at your face, It was hilarious!"
      ],
      [
        "[He] chuckles, trying not to get caught by the teacher."
      ],
      [
        " I chuckle too, not trying to make a fuss about something so small,"
      ],
      [
        "but I place my hand where [Fabian] had flicked me. It kinda hurts."
      ],
      [
        "Class continues and I try to focus, but now I feel more bummed out than before."
      ],
      [
        " sigh as I lean on my hand and write down what’s written on the whiteboard. "
      ],
      [
        "I feel a tug on my shirt as [Fabián] slides his notebook to me."
      ],
      [
        "I take a better look and there’s a drawing of our teacher as a fat chicken. "
      ],
      [
        "I try not to burst out laughing and drown a chuckle in my hands."
      ],
      [
        "It suddenly becomes even more impossible as [Fabian] begins to make chicken noises."
      ],
      [
        "I roll my eyes and smile. Forgetting what had me sad a couple minutes ago."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] could be really funny when [he] wanted to."
      ],
      [
        "That is something that makes my tummy fill with butterflies everytime [he] makes me laugh."
      ],
      [
        "Even more time of class passed, and [Fabian] and I were finishing writing on"
      ],
      [
        "our notebooks as the bell rings."
      ],
      [
        "I stretch in my place, tired of the hours of class I had to"
      ],
      [
        "endure just to get a stupid title that will for sure help me place a well-paying job."
      ],
      [
        "What a bunch of bologna."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] turns to me with the same tiredness in [his] eyes. "
      ],
      [
        "Yo, wanna come eat with me? I know a fantastic place nearby."
      ],
      [
        "My stomach grumbles loudly before I can protest."
      ],
      [
        "So I just nod and get up from my seat."
      ],
      [
        "Better be someplace delicious, you hear me?"
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] takes me to a plaza in the opposite direction of the path I always take to my home."
      ],
      [
        " It’s small, but has a lot of nice fast-food establishments. "
      ],
      [
        "The variety actually makes it hard to decide what I want to eat. "
      ],
      [
        "Ta-da! this is where I come to eat almost everyday."
      ],
      [
        "Just don’t tell anyone, I like the solitude of this place at this hour."
      ],
      [
        "No worries, you’ll be the only one I’ll come here with. I promise."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] scratches [his] head and looks away with a blush on [his] face."
      ],
      [
        "It looks like [he] really gets bashful when there’s other people around us when I flirt with [him]. "
      ],
      [
        "Even if there’s just a few…"
      ],
      [
        "S-so, what do you want to eat?"
      ],
      [
        "Ain’t it obvious? I’ll have a hamburguer. I’m up for something tasty."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] looks at me and smiles. We both go up to the burger stall and"
      ],
      [
        "place our order."
      ],
      [
        "My food was done rather quickly, so I wait for a little while until [Fabian] comes and sits with me."
      ],
      [
        "As we both are enjoying our food, [he] looks at me and tilts [his] head."
      ],
      [
        "Hey, now that I think about it, I don’t know much about you, don’t I?"
      ],
      [
        "Tell me something about yourself..."
      ],
      [
        "Oh! haha… what can I say? uh…"
      ]
    ],
